long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Do you like an arcade games? Double Stickman is an easy yet addictive game. Make both Stickman hop on platforms and stay strong.

Stickmen like to sprint, and hopping is, for them, a national sport. And this is not random because most stickman world consists of platforms. Heroes invite you to contests where the main thing is not the acceleration but the ability to persist. Simultaneously, two runners will go to beat the platform valley. You have a challenging task - to keep the path of both. Click on the lower and upper characters so they can hop and be on a secure platform. If you skip, both stickers will be in the loser, as you are with them.

Click the stickman with mouse


To swipe Install this extension to play the Double Stickman game or offline with no additional downloads and no ads. 

You can contact us at support@724fun.com and share your thoughts and problems

After clicking the add the game to chrome button, you can find the game in the extensions section. If you wish, you can visit 724fun.com. If you wish, you can play again and if you want to remove it, you can remove it from the extensions section.
